thread.title: Jan-Eric
thread.title_full: The Logo Company reviewed by Jan-Eric

author: Jan-Eric
title: Jan-Eric
text: When you are doing design work online, based on your words only, and not being able to sit down or express the feeling about how a logo should look an feel like you get a bit worried. However, after my simple explanation to what I was looking for and some great suggestions coming back from the designers, I was really happy with the result. I know if I would have meet up a designer it would have costed me 4 times more and the result would probably have been the same. Good job!
